'''Lara Sousa''' kandi '''Lara de Sousa''' numukinnyi wa firime wa Mozambike. <ref name="ONavio">https://m.bizcommunity.com/Article/196/482/208260.html</ref> <ref name="BC">https://www.britishcouncil.org/arts/sub-saharan-africa/colabnownow/2019</ref> Yakoze nka porogarama muri Festival ya DOCKANEMA [[Mozambike|documentaire ya Mozambike]] imyaka itari mike kandi akora ibikorwa byimibereho niterambere, yibanda kubushakashatsi bwe kubibazo byuburinganire, uburenganzira bwa muntu nibindi. <ref name="Fin">https://www.ethnofest.gr/film/fin/</ref>

== Uburezi ==
Sousa afite impamyabumenyi yihariye mu bijyanye na Documentaire Direction, yakuye muri Escuela Internacional de Cine y Televiziyo(EICTV) ya San Antonio de los Baños, [[Kiba|Cuba]] . Yize kandi Anthropology muri ISCTE, [[Porutigali|Porutugali]] na UCM, [[Esipanye|Espanye]], azobereye muri Visual Anthropology .  <ref>http://miradasdoc.com/mdoc2019/portfolio_page/o-navio-e-o-mar/?lang=en</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2017, yanditse, ayobora kandi asohora inyandiko yerekana [[Icyesipanyole|ururimi rw'icyesipanyoli]] '', La Finca del Miedo'' (Umurima w'ubwoba), yakozwe na IECTV, muri [[Kiba|Cuba]] . <ref name="La">https://www.berlinale-talents.de/bt/project/profile/228964</ref>

Muri 2018, yayoboye filime documentaire, ''Fin'' (End), nayo yasohotse muri Cuba. 

Filime documentaire, ''The Ship and the Sea'' ( [[Igiporutigali|Igiporutugali:]] ''O Navio eo Mar'' ), yakoranye na Matheus Mello, afatanya na Everlane Moraes, yatoranijwe hamwe nizindi firime zigera kuri 30 nkumushinga wimishinga yimari kuri Durban ya 11 Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime (DIFF 2020) ryabaye hagati ya 10 na 20 Nzeri, kumurongo. <ref>http://africultures.com/evenements/?no=49687</ref> <ref>https://ladima.africa/durban-filmmart-institute-announces-2020-durban-filmmart-finance-forum-projects/</ref> <ref>https://sandtonchronicle.co.za/lnn/1141451/31-film-projects-across-africa-selected-to-pitch-at-durban-filmmarts-finance-forum</ref> Iyi filime yatsindiye kandi muri Durban FilmMart ya 2020, Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime Amashusho Amsterdam (IDFA) Igihembo [[Ubuholandi|cy’Ubuholandi]] .  <ref>https://www.idfa.nl/en/info/project-award-winners-at-idfa-2020</ref>

Yitabiriye gutoranya ibikorwa bya Indaba 2020, mu cyiciro cya mbere, "Abitabiriye 2020 bafite imishinga ni abaproducer", hamwe na Inadelso Costa umushinga wa firime witwa "Karigana". <ref>https://iffr.com/en/blog/indaba-announces-its-inaugural-selection</ref>

Yitabiriye imurikagurisha rya Colab NowNow ryateguwe n’inama y’Ubwongereza, afatanya n’umunsi mukuru wa Maputo Fast Forward wa [[Mozambike|Mozambique]] na Fak'ugesi African Digital Innovation Festival yo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika yepfo]] .  <ref>https://festival-mff.com/exposicoes/colabnownow/</ref>

